        "type": "equation",
        "title": "PED (point)",
        "latex": "E_d = \\frac{\\%\\Delta Q_d}{\\%\\Delta P} = \\frac{dQ}{dP}\\cdot\\frac{P}{Q}"
      },
      {
        "type": "equation",
        "title": "Arc elasticity",
        "latex": "E_d^{\\text{arc}} = \\frac{(Q_2-Q_1)/(Q_1+Q_2)}{(P_2-P_1)/(P_1+P_2)}"
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "title": "|E_d| interpretation",
        "markdown": "| |E_d| | Demand |\n|-------|--------|\n| > 1 | Elastic |\n| = 1 | Unit elastic |\n| < 1 | Inelastic |"
